      • apply

        public void apply(DwGLTexture src_luminance,
                  DwGLTexture dst_bloom,
                  DwGLTexture dst_composition)
        "src_luminance" serves as the source texture for the bloom pass. e.g this texture can be the result of a brightness-prepass on dst_composition. "dst_bloom" is the merged result of several iterations of gaussian-blurs. "dst_composition" is the final result of additive blending with "dst_bloom".
        Parameters:
        src_luminance -
        dst_bloom -
        dst_composition -
